      <title>捷克通胀率超过预期，央行发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/czech-inflation-exceeds-forecasts-as-central-bank-flags-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国上个月的通货膨胀率超出预期，这进一步增加了央行对降息保持谨慎态度的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/czech-inflation-exceeds-forecasts-as-central-bank-flags-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
